  "texts": [
    "There is a direct relationship between the thickness of the rings and the number of citations during the same time period.",
    "Colder color tones indicate earlier publication dates.",
    "The size of the nodes is positively correlated with the quantity of research literature originating from each country.",
    "Larger nodes indicate a higher volume of research literature from that specific country.",
    "The results of the analysis demonstrate that Germany occupies the leading position among countries with a significant number of collaborative publications, followed by France, the UK, and Italy."
